OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,FHeavy rain at the start of the year
OL,8,Fcaused a spike in drivers hitting
OL,9,Fpotholes hidden in puddles, new
OL,10,Ffigures suggest.
OL,12,FThe RAC said the daily average number
OL,13,Fof pothole reports it received from
OL,14,Fbroken-down drivers in February was
OL,15,Fthree-and-a-half times higher than the
OL,16,Fsame month last year.
OL,18,FIt attributed this to the "incredible
OL,19,Famount of standing water" on roads
OL,20,Fwhich was "hiding potholes".
OL,26,@zD@[OU{D@YO]|D@KOU|D@[O]
