OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,FProvisional Met Office statistics show
OL,8,FEngland received 42% more rain than
OL,9,Fusual between December and February,
OL,10,Fas a string of low-pressure weather
OL,11,Fsystems moved across the UK from the
OL,12,FAtlantic, with repeated outbreaks of
OL,13,Fwet and windy conditions.
OL,15,FThe downpours were particularly
OL,16,Fpronounced across southern and central
OL,17,FEngland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
