OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773151902
OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,FThe RAC said 6,290 of its members
OL,8,Fmentioned potholes when logging
OL,9,Fbreakdowns last month, compared with
OL,10,F1,842 in February 2025.
OL,12,FJanuary saw 5,106 mentions at a daily
OL,13,Faverage of 165, up from 63 in the same
OL,14,Fmonth last year.
OL,16,FCommon vehicle problems caused by
OL,17,Fpotholes include damaged shock
OL,18,Fabsorbers, broken suspension springs
OL,19,Fand distorted wheels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
