OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,FRAC head of policy Simon Williams
OL,8,Fsaid: "In February there was an
OL,9,Fincredible amount of standing water
OL,10,Fand puddles on our roads, many of
OL,11,Fwhich were hiding potholes which sadly
OL,12,Ftoo many drivers fell foul of.
OL,14,F"While this amount of rain is hard for
OL,15,Fthe saturated land to cope with, the
OL,16,FRAC suspects that poor drainage may
OL,17,Falso be to blame, possibly as a result
OL,18,Fof councils not carrying out as much
OL,19,Fof these works as they have done in
OL,20,Fthe past."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
