OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,FRAC figures show a repair bill for a
OL,8,Fcar suffering pothole damage more
OL,9,Fserious than a puncture can reach #590.
OL,11,FTom Hunt, who chairs the Local
OL,12,FGovernment Association's inclusive
OL,13,Fgrowth committee, said: "Councils are
OL,14,Fvery aware of the recent and
OL,15,Fpersistent rainfall and the impact on
OL,16,Flocal highways.
OL,18,F"Local teams are working hard to fix
OL,19,Fpotholes swiftly.
OL,26,@uD@YOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773151902
OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,F"However, many factors affect how
OL,8,Fquickly roads can be fixed, including
OL,9,Fthe weather, safety risks, the type of
OL,10,Froad and traffic levels, to budget
OL,11,Fpressures.
OL,13,F"We urge members of the public to
OL,14,Fcontinue to report potholes and other
OL,15,Froad damage."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
