OL,3,CWet start to year causes surge in
OL,4,Cdrivers hitting potholes hidden by
OL,5,Cpuddles
OL,7,FA Department for Transport
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "We are providing
OL,9,Fcouncils with a record #7.3 billion
OL,10,Fover the next four years to help them
OL,11,Ftackle potholes, and it's now over to
OL,12,Fthem to get on with maintaining and
OL,13,Fupgrading their roads.
OL,15,F"Our new council rating system charts
OL,16,Fhow well they are delivering for local
OL,17,Fpeople, including their long-term
OL,18,Ffixes rather than just patching up
OL,19,Fpotholes."
OL,26,@pD@TOUwD@AOU{D@JO]
